WEBVTT

00:01.520 --> 00:03.870
When I Grow Up

00:05.250 --> 00:07.740
What are the people's jobs?

00:07.740 --> 00:10.210
Let's meet them in the town.

00:11.270 --> 00:12.640
(한 남자가 노래하고 있다.)

00:12.640 --> 00:15.580
I sing songs.

00:15.580 --> 00:18.110
Guess my job.

00:18.110 --> 00:20.740
I'm a singer.

00:20.740 --> 00:22.450
La la la~~

00:23.410 --> 00:23.890
(한 여자가 그림을 그리고 있다.)

00:23.890 --> 00:26.980
I paint pictures.

00:26.980 --> 00:29.380
Guess my job.

00:29.380 --> 00:32.310
I'm an artist.

00:33.290 --> 00:34.050
(한 남자가 아이를 진찰하고 있다.)

00:34.050 --> 00:37.730
I take care of sick people.

00:37.730 --> 00:40.540
Guess my job.

00:40.540 --> 00:42.460
I'm a doctor.

00:43.140 --> 00:43.690
(한 여자가 빵을 굽고 있다.)

00:43.690 --> 00:47.970
I bake delicious bread.

00:47.970 --> 00:50.660
Guess my job.

00:50.660 --> 00:52.310
I'm a baker.

00:53.010 --> 00:53.930
(한 여자가 버스를 운전하고 있다.)

00:53.930 --> 00:58.210
I take people to different places.

00:58.210 --> 01:01.580
Guess my job.

01:01.580 --> 01:03.590
I'm a bus driver.

01:05.830 --> 01:08.610
What do you want to be in the future?
